Subject: [PATCH 1696/1825] fix: alp: avoid board configuration conflict (PON
 serdes expanderNum)

https://github.com/MISL-EBU-System-SW/misl-windriver.git linux-3.4.69-14t2-read
commit 80dabfbc8fcfa1aa874fc1d2b27a2f4b7223c479

	Before this fix, there was a conflict between PON serdes config, and Serdes Lane#1 config.
	this issue is fixed by updating regNum and expanderNum of PON serdes config.
	Update the regNum to be 0, and expanderNum to be 1
	(the ponserdes use the third 8 bits in the EEPROM)

